estic mountains and lush forests. The rhythmic strokes of the oars create a soothing harmony, while the stillness of the water mirrors the tranquility of the surroundings. Nature's symphony of chirping birds and rustling leaves accompanies this idyllic journey, where the world slows down, and peace reigns.", "short_description": "Relax yourself in a virtual reality tour across a gentle mountain river"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.polyrawdevelopment.com/Policy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "PolyrawDevelopment", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.polyrawdevelopment.com/", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2837265163266059", "context_category": "ENTERTAINMENT"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "687057922013375"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ADVENTURE", "EXPLORATION", "SIMULATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["GAMEPAD"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1241637220103230"}, "review_messages": ["", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982674_284401375511883_108529846430203904_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=kTxCMEImyXAQ7kNvgHc8nh_&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=A5OY3Fq57SpcJn6Ub4Jz8Nn&oh=00_AYCKF2Tm7FfR-ANWJo56PEYwU4zMSWpFzcxoEURz2k-79w&oe=66F560E0"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "RelaxRiver", "platform": "ANDROID", "context_category": {"context_category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "id": "2837265163266059"}, "context_topics": [{"topic_nam